{
  "title": "Moist Springy Uruguayan Baguette Sandwich",
  "description": "A buttery and springy sandwich featuring sous-vide cooked ingredients and a monsoon Uruguayan twist, served on a crispy baguette, this dish is shojin-friendly and perfect for a quick lunch",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
  "diet": [
